title: Vem dödade Agneta? - Mysteriet i Mistekärr
overview: One autumn day in 2008, 63-year-old Agneta is found beaten to death by a lake in Småland. Suspicion quickly falls on Agneta's husband Ingemar, but is he really guilty? The locals hover in uncertainty until the case takes an unexpected turn, just over a year later. Who killed Agneta?
